    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Just played a little bit with react-native, here the list of what I observe for it to work: \n- [ ] we need a proper interface that will expose only connectors \n- [ ] we need an InstantSearch version that will use the algoliasearch for react-native client\n- [ ] currently we are using `process.nextTick` on the createWidgetsManager (for update). It needs a polyfill on the react-native side in order to work. \n",
