    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Nice!\n\nAs for process.nextTick usage, I am not even sure this is needed/consequences versus a simple setTimeout(fn, 0). I would go for the later to ease the work\n\nBeing able to use react-instantsearch (connectors + `<InstantSearch>`) on react-native on day one would be awesome news!\n",
