    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "As for the interface we expose, we had some discussion, we could do this:\n\n``` js\nimport {connectRefinementList} from 'react-instantsearch'; // platform agnostic\nimport {InstantSearch, RangeSlider} from 'react-instantsearch/dom'; // platform specific\nimport {InstantSearch} from 'react-instantsearch/native'; // platform specific\n```\n\n`InstantSearch` being platform specific because of the need to have a different algolia http client instantiated. And ultimately things like urlSync=true and createURL may not be working nor have the good semantics for a native platform (where we would maybe only talk about \"routing\" rather than url, dunno here).\n",
    "created_at": "2016-10-17T09:56:08Z",
